  "texts": [
    "WebThinker includes a synthetic report-generation dataset (GLAVE), but evaluation relies solely on LLM-judge ten-scale evaluations (e.g., \"comprehensiveness\") without explicit citation or evidence checks.",
    "We only consider proprietary systems that provide an API for their deep research systems at the time of writing, which excludes Gemini Deep Research and Grok Deep Research.",
